---
// ─── 页头导航（毛玻璃风格） ───
import ThemeToggle from '@/components/ThemeToggle.tsx';
import { BASE, SITE_NAME } from '@/lib/constants';

const NAV_ITEMS = [
  { href: BASE, label: '首页' },
  { href: `${BASE}blog`, label: '文章' },
  { href: `${BASE}projects`, label: '项目' },
  { href: `${BASE}friends`, label: '友链' },
  { href: `${BASE}timeline`, label: '归档' },
  { href: `${BASE}about`, label: '关于' },
];
---

<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 glass-card rounded-none border-x-0 border-t-0">
  <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-3">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <a
      href={BASE}
      class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight transition-all hover:scale-105"
      style="font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;"
    >
      <span class="text-gradient-brand">
        {SITE_NAME}
      </span>
    </a>

    <!-- 桌面导航 -->
    <div class="hidden items-center gap-1 md:flex">
      {NAV_ITEMS.map((item) => (
        <a
          href={item.href}
          class="rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))] transition-all hover:text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] hover:bg-[hsl(var(--primary))/0.1]"
        >
          {item.label}
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- ThemeToggle + 移动菜单按钮 -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <ThemeToggle client:load />
      <button
        id="mobile-menu-btn"
        class="glass-button rounded-lg p-2 md:hidden"
        aria-label="打开菜单"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="4" x2="20" y1="12" y2="12" />
          <line x1="4" x2="20" y1="6" y2="6" />
          <line x1="4" x2="20" y1="18" y2="18" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- 移动端下拉菜单 -->
  <div
    id="mobile-menu"
    class="hidden border-t border-[hsl(var(--border))] px-4 py-3 md:hidden"
  >
    {NAV_ITEMS.map((item) => (
      <a
        href={item.href}
        class="block rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))] hover:bg-[hsl(var(--primary))/0.1] hover:text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] transition-colors"
      >
        {item.label}
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>
</header>

<script>
  // 移动端菜单开关
  const btn = document.getElementById('mobile-menu-btn');
  const menu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
  if (btn && menu) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      menu.classList.toggle('hidden');
    });
  }
</script>
